        <Parent_String>camps (recreation areas) [300000517], recreation areas [300000510], complexes by function [300000203], complexes (buildings and sites) [300000202], Built Complexes and Districts (hierarchy name) [300000201], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
